OL,3,CBodies of three women recovered from
OL,4,Cthe sea in Brighton, police confirm
OL,6,FThe bodies of three women have been
OL,7,Frecovered from the sea in Brighton.
OL,9,FSussex Police confirmed the bodies
OL,10,Fwere pulled from the water near
OL,11,FMadeira Drive on Brighton seafront
OL,12,Fearly on Wednesday.
OL,14,FA large police presence remains at the
OL,15,Fscene.
