OL,3,CBodies of three women recovered from
OL,4,Cthe sea in Brighton, police confirm
OL,6,FChief Superintendent Adam Hays from
OL,7,FSussex Police said: "This is a tragic
OL,8,Fincident and fast-moving enquiries are
OL,9,Fongoing to confirm the identities of
OL,10,Fthese three women and understand
OL,11,Fexactly what has happened.
OL,13,F"I know this is concerning for the
OL,14,Fcommunity, but I would ask the public
OL,15,Fto stay away from the scene at this
OL,16,Ftime while emergency services continue
OL,17,Ftheir work.
OL,19,F"We will provide further updates as
OL,20,Fsoon as they are available."
